  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Designated premises scheme: letter to directors of adult social services
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  

  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">The letter sets out arrangements for the Care Quality Commission designated premises scheme for people discharged to a care home with a positive COVID-19 test. </p>

  </div>
</div>

